name: Me, Myself and I
description:
A little lesson that being alone physically does not mean you're alone in reality.






GAME CREATED FOR BRACKEY'S 2022 GAME JAM. 
It's short but I only made it for learning experience and in no way was in it for the competition, Game jams are made for one to learn and push themselves in a restricted time :)

Game suck I know don't judge.
